---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
	<section class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About the Conference</h1>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="grid-layout">
                <main>
                    <h2>100 Years of Stafford Beer</h2>
                    <p>The ‘100 Years of Stafford Beer’ project will include the development of:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>A video documentary:</strong> ‘A 100 Years of Stafford Beer: A documentary celebrating the visionary who fused science, art, and spirit to reimagine society’.</li>
                        <li><strong>A Festschrift Book:</strong> An online edited book with contributions from invited authors to summarize Stafford’s legacy.</li>
                        <li><strong>Metaphorum Journal Launch:</strong> ‘Organisational Systems’ - an online, open-source journal.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>Who We Are Inviting</h2>
                    <p>We welcome:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Relatives and collaborators</strong> who knew Stafford personally and will share insights into his life and character.</li>
                        <li><strong>Researchers</strong> advancing his legacy by adapting his original thinking and developing innovative cybersystemic methodologies.</li>
                        <li><strong>Consultants and practitioners</strong> who continue to evolve his theories through creative and impactful applications.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>Conference Steering Committee</h2>
                    <ul class="committee-list">
                        <li>Angela Espinosa</li>
                        <li>Jon Walker</li>
                        <li>Ayham Fattoum</li>
                        <li>Juliana Alves</li>
                        <li>Camilo Osejo</li>
                        <li>Stephen Harwood</li>
                        <li>Iffat Sabir</li>
                    </ul>
                </main>
                
                <aside>
                    <div class="info-box">
                        <h3>Pre-Conference Events</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Session at ST&SP Conference:</strong> 24–26 March 2026.</li>
                            <li><strong>Special Stream at ISSS:</strong> June 2026.</li>
                            <li><strong>Special Stream at ASC (Brazil):</strong> 2-7 August 2026.</li>
                            <li><strong>Special Stream at ORS (Nottingham):</strong> Sept 8th-10th 2026.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    .page-header {
        background: var(--color-primary);
        color: white;
        padding: 3rem 0;
    }

    .grid-layout {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        margin-top: 2rem;
        font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    ul {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .committee-list {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .info-box {
        background: var(--color-background-alt);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border-top: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    }

    .info-box h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .info-box ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .info-box li {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .grid-layout {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>
